- [ ] Save/Update persists data to backend; on success, UI shows confirmation and updated run state; on failure, error messaging is clear.
- [ ] Run Details page loads with inputs, trace, logs, artifacts, timing, and outcomes; supports revert action where applicable.
- [ ] All array/object usage guards against null/undefined values per runtime safety rules.

